{"tid":1603643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想再有前線手足被大規模咁咬 請買呢樣物資","createTime":"2019-09-29T17:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T08:12:56.000Z","uid":294763,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"91bed0305f2a6faac52c2a8c43250c4889da1c8c","tid":1603643,"uid":294763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:25:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>麻繩路障</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日PP對出, 對手既戰術就係於大道放TG引前線注意<br />\n然後再有一堆收埋左畜生跑出黎包夾, 好似呢段片咁<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/blader/status/1178247973345484800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fblader%2Fstatus%2F1178247973345484800&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrer6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=df361738\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fblader%2Fstatus%2F1178247973345484800&h=0c14e31c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/blader/status/1178247973345484800</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><ins>點解需要用麻繩做路障?</ins></em></strong><br />\n原因1. <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>呢家唔會再有鐵馬</strong></span><br />\n原因2.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 拆鐵欄太哂時間, 要起碼10個三角型先封到一條路, 姐係要拆30個鐵欄,</span></strong> 不符合時間成本效益, 近幾次未見過有鐵欄陣<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><ins>點用?</ins></em></strong><br />\n其實每個路口都仲有鐵欄, 燈柱, 只要可以縛到既物件都可能用 包括樹<br />\n拉到直一直再縛個死結<br />\n示意圖: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QLPwNau.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQLPwNau.png&h=71a99e01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有幾密封幾密<br />\n <br />\n雖然對家用刀可以破解<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但麻繩路障目的唔係作為堅固既防守<br />\n而係用黎爭取時間, 等班狗冇咁易就直路狂奔出黎包夾, 特別係分岔路<br />\n防止今日PP既突擊再次出現</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以請所有人幫手買麻繩, 有幾粗得幾粗</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">物資List 請加入麻繩</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請確保係邊境使用, 唔好阻住手足</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nP牌仔推唔到 求大家幫手推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"482c53807d6c4933048c4831642953b8a6163758","tid":1603643,"uid":293310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:28:00.000Z","msg":"Spiderman"},{"pid":"1e0c933a45cbe2086725ff18e2cb85e083db9f5e","tid":1603643,"uid":1400,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:28:19.000Z","msg":"用魚絲綁柱唔係仲好咩"},{"pid":"f0777555fdefff6c23e83edf69215271759a540a","tid":1603643,"uid":260460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e0c933a45cbe2086725ff18e2cb85e083db9f5e","tid":1603643,"uid":1400,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:28:19.000Z","msg":"用魚絲綁柱唔係仲好咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:31:31.000Z","msg":"魚絲都可以, 但前提係要前邊冇手足, 如果唔係kick死手足"},{"pid":"ef9dfe14793ca18c43d198f86d65e87d5979eda6","tid":1603643,"uid":190730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:33:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7366dacf0d67d2020f60d780cfb59edcb346aad1","tid":1603643,"uid":232671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:34:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1730db50c5b69f0aa2881874104f84f1cec5ca64","tid":1603643,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:35:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ccc1e45f2a84dd90077a8019898d2a3a5c2ed6e","tid":1603643,"uid":74959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:45:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6310357fb1073d0d24fd581e95d47a7017c8c19b","tid":1603643,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:47:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23288de019b7ed60f4e64679e7d3abcbbf350e76","tid":